## Integration Points

### Relationship to Writer Agents
Strong writer agents (Nicolas Cole, Shaan Puri, Tobias Allen, Lara Acosta, Harry Dry, Cardinal Mason) already produce structurally unpredictable, human-sounding content. **Do not run their output through this skill** — it would flatten their distinctive voices.

This skill exists for the gaps:
- Raw AI output with no writer applied
- Speed-mode content where you skip the full writer pipeline
- Professional/academic contexts with aggressive AI detection

### Chain Architecture
```
[Writer Agent used?]
  ├─ YES → [Writer Skill] → draft → ship (skip humanization)
  └─ NO  → [Raw AI draft] → [Predictability Audit] → [Humanization Pass if needed] → ship
```

This skill is a **safety net**, not a mandatory post-processor. Diagnose first, treat only when needed.

